{
  "stem": "3685.2",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And during-- in the army, I knew, I knew German.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I knew German-- not fluently, because I learned when I worked for them in that grenzschutzkommando in Strzemilcze-- that the border patrol.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I learned the language, I'm good on languages.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I, I was trained by the Russian army.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was trained in engineering-- setting up mines, and taking up mines and taking out.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So that was a very dangerous job.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I-- they were looking for interpreter.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They hired me.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And that's how I lived through the war.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Till-- and then, after the war, I got, I got discharged.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Actually, I was in the occupation force in Germany.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But when they found out that my father was in Canada, they transferred me to Siberia.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It's close to Ural.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It's close to Siberia.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And there, I got-- I was there six months.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I got discharged.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "After I got discharged, I didn't have a place where to go.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So I went to my-- not to that village.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I went to a place called Lopatyn-- L-O-P-A-T-Y-N.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "That Lopatyn was like the district from our village.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Went there, and I start working.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I had to work.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So I was given a job with [? heights. ?] I didn't have a clue what, what to do.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "But I learned.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I was getting the [? heights ?] from the farmers.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Worked for the government, then sort them, then specify them which sort, and sent them back.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And I work there for a year and a half.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, yeah.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I can tell you a lot, but--",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, I can tell you experiences, experiences, which-- like for instance, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] OK experiences from my services.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "This-- we-- I blew up a bridge with two other guys.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "OK?",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
